<title>
Brake Discs and Pads Inspection
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove wheel and caliper but do not disconnect brake hose from caliper.
</ptxt>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Check disc brake pads and discs for excessive wear, damage and deflection. Replace parts if necessary. 
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Be sure to torque caliper pin bolts to specification.
</ptxt>
